# Input

```scss
$my-map: (
  'foo': 1, // Comment
  'bar': 2, // Comment
);

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,5 +1,4 @@
 $my-map: (
-  "foo": 1,
-  // Comment
+  "foo": 1, // Comment
   "bar": 2, // Comment
 );
```

# Output

```scss
$my-map: (
  "foo": 1, // Comment
  "bar": 2, // Comment
);
```
